  <brief_title>PTSD Prevention Study Examining the Efficacy of Sertraline in Burn Victims</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Pilot Study of Sertraline for the Prevention of PTSD in Burn Victims</official_title>
  <sponsors>
