  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study to determine whether
      administration of sertraline to patients who exhibit acute stress disorder secondary to
      severe burns can contribute to the prevention of post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
